description: API to generate one time URL to access some web services in the partner

parameters.name: member_id
parameters.description: Request's unique identifier for a merchant

parameters.name: auto_type
parameters.description: The timestamp when the valid end date will be generated

parameters.name: expire_time
parameters.description: The deadline to an API request for every sharing

parameters.name: type
parameters.description: This is to indicate whether the link is once time link or share. If the user's type is once time link then user can only visit the web service when URL is accessed once

error_codes.description: There is no partner_id in param

notes: The documentation includes several error codes and their descriptions, as well as request/response examples. The API appears to be part of an OpenWeLink system for generating one-time access URLs for partner services.
